items.title: Awesome Computational Biology
items.content_text:
### Databases / Compound

*   [Drug Repurposing Hub](https://repo-hub.broadinstitute.org/repurposing#download-data) - Collections of drug repurposing data containing drug, moa, target etc.

### Databases / Protein

*   [AlphaFold Protein Structure Database](https://alphafold.ebi.ac.uk/api-docs) - Database of 3D protein structures.

### Databases / Interaction

*   Protein-Protein Interaction
    *   [STRING](https://string-db.org/) - Protein-Protein Interaction Networks for several organisms.
    *   [BioGRID](https://thebiogrid.org/) - Database of Protein, Genetic and Chemical Interactions.
    *   [HIPPIE](http://cbdm-01.zdv.uni-mainz.de/~mschaefer/hippie/) - Human Protein-Protein Interaction database.
items.content_html:
Databases / Compound

items.title: Awesome Machine Learning
items.content_text:
### Python / Natural Language Processing

*   [CometLLM (⭐11k)](https://github.com/comet-ml/comet-llm) - Track, log, visualize and evaluate your LLM prompts and prompt chains.
*   [Transformers (⭐147k)](https://github.com/huggingface/transformers) - A deep learning library containing thousands of pre-trained models on different tasks. The goto place for anything related to Large Language Models.

items.title: Awesome Docker
items.content_text:
### Terminal / Terminal UI
